title: CCK Podcast: Dog Days
description:
It is the first official Dog Day of Quarantine. Joe Buck might have a paid porn subscription. Who would you want to do play-by-play in the bedroom? Too Hot To Handle on Netflix. What would happen if The Rocket got hacked? Wearing real clothes in Quarantine. Name that blogger. Catty company emails. Where is Neil today?


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
